author: kevin-m
msg: Changed columnType from DATETIME to TIMESTAMP to support PostgreSQL. MySQL and HSQLDB still work.
Encoded string contained a "T", needed to update offsets from "hour", etc,  in valueAsDBString.
PostgreSQL does not store millisecond information - needed to update setFromDBColumn.
